org.silex.runtime.domObject.js.ContainerDOMObject

type
class
extends
org.silex.runtime.domObject.base.ContainerDOMObjectBase
This is the JavaScript implementation of the container DOMObject. When it's semantic is set, it adds the JavaScript specific behaviour of changing the root node type of the reference to the native DOM by setting it's name

Constructor

new(?referenceToNativeDOMObject : js.HtmlDom)
